<b>Usage Notes:</b><br>
TO IMPORT FROM EXCEL: YOU MUST SAVE THE DATA AS CSV in Excel, to do this please select [File] and [Save As] and change the type to "Text/CSV". 
If you attempt to re-import the native Excel file that was exported it will absolutely corrupt your product database.<br>
<P>
Customers using Netscape, Opera, or Mac OS should save the CSV file and open it in the application of their choice (Filemaker, etc).<P>
